   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Mentoring Club, Uganda: Making Education Count</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ADOVIC, a grass-roots social change organization based in Jinja, Uganda recently completed a successful six month pilot programme, mentoring 22 high school students. ADOVIC now seeks funding to make their programme, &apos;The Mentoring Club&apos;, available to schools across the Busoga Region.  You can help make a difference to students&apos; long term emotional wellbeing and educational success while also providing opportunities for local youth and social worker university graduates. Join us now at The Club!</narrative>
  </description>
